title.oldValue: Microsoft Teams: Give Feedback for GCC
title.newValue: Microsoft Teams: Give Feedback for GCC and GCCH

description.oldValue: Users in GCC can give feedback via the Help icon in Teams regarding their experience with the product. This drives how Microsoft addresses trends and influences future features and product updates. From the help icon, click on give feedback to provide verbatims on your product experience.
description.newValue: Users in GCC and GCCH can give feedback via the Help icon in Teams regarding their experience with the product. This drives how Microsoft addresses trends and influences future features and product updates. From the help icon, click on give feedback to provide verbatims on your product experience.
